description: Experience penthouse living in this stunning duplex, ideally located in the vibrant South Boston/Fort Point corridor. Just off W. Broadway and steps from the Harborwalk, this top-floor home offers 1,300+ sq. ft. of open-concept living with 2 bedrooms, 2 full baths, abundant natural light and high ceilings on both levels. The spacious living and dining area features a custom built-in media unit, while the kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, abundance of cabinet space, and gas cooking. The primary suite includes a recently redone en-suite bath and large closet, while the second bedroom offers great space. Private roof deck, perfect for lounging, grilling, and entertaining. Additional features include central A/C, in-unit laundry, another outdoor space off of the kitchen, bike storage room, and direct-access deeded garage parking with ample storage space. Prime location near the Broadway T (Red Line), major highways, top restaurants, and markets, including Foodie’s and Whole Foods.
